EDIT: Friday Frontpage once more! Thanks a lot, Imgurians! I do reviews as a hobby, this week I analyzed "Breakfast of Champions" by Kurt Vonnegut! And this time I had the guest appearance of Mr. Sunday! And a bit of a guest appearance by Miss Jellybean. You can watch the review here https://youtu.be/2B1Dwr29JXc</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/UUTcmgi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Skullwriter]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Don't screw up, don't screw up, don't screw up</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/FnzEolQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aKe45at.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After about 5-6 years, I'm coming up on the end of the LitRPG, SciFi/Fantasy story I've been writing. It's been a lot of work, worry, and more work, but I'm almost there. I just have to not screw it up.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iWLAtqB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Things have gone much better than I hoped! I never thought I'd have made it this far, but thanks to some very kind people online (including a lot of imgurians), my series has found an audience.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GlgKnex.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I'm not gonna lie, this has all been very difficult. Tons of self-doubt, watching people younger than me do better than me in a shorter amount of time, worrying that I'm not making enough money to justify the time I spend writing... it's tough.

I only started because my wife sent me an imgur post of another indie author on their way. So if you're an author, artist, or whatever else, and you're looking for a sign to put yourself out there, then hey, this is it. 

This post ( https://imgur.com/gallery/as-author-its-hard-telling-other-people-about-work-hvE3uXC ) also convinced me to just go for it. I like my work, and I now know that others like it too. I don't advertise myself much (I mostly post cursed image albums), but it's part of the job. It never gets easy, and I'm always nervous, but it does get less difficult.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Pd5GC7e.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MQ6OtmN.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you've made it all the way down here and read my spiel, thanks. These are my books. I've got one more to go, and God willing, I won't fumble it. 
My cover artist is Enzo Fernandez aka pkblitz on most social media sites. All his work and my own are 100% human generated. Fuck AI slop.

Currently, the books are on sale here: https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BCQKXVVL
If you'd like to follow me, I'm online at the following places:
BlueSky (meme shitposting and photos of my dogs): https://bsky.app/profile/jjackerknecht.com
TikTok (I just started one at the behest of an author friend telling me to get off my ass and just do it already): https://www.tiktok.com/@jjackerknecht
Personal Website (Gonna try to update the blog more): https://www.jjackerknecht.com/</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/u3TM594.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dog and donkey tax.
Thanks for all the support thus far, imgur.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/FnzEolQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[EmperorJustin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Too soon?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DwwlOKl</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NfZeyKV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Same sex marriage is just as legit as other marriages</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DwwlOKl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Shenaniganz80]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Rachel Maddow (@maddowshow) – Rachel runs through Donald Trump's dizzying ambivalence toward the U.S. allies he seems to love to insult, but whose help he also seems to realize he needs to defend the Strait of Hormuz</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/el90LEQ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RICF5Md.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/el90LEQ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OceansRust]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Periodt</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qe4Ubzi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/m9QMUUZ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qe4Ubzi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[BaddieVillain]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Donald in 90s</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5pJv3EW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SOPr03p.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5pJv3EW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[wafflesdidit]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I'm a simple woman, I hear funny accents, I laugh</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aVvmtVY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9rl4VgT.gif" style